name: Wisteria Swap
description: The most crucial thing in DeFi service is to be safe from rug-pull, and it must be a service model that can cope with inflation. WisteriaSwap proved its safe and sustainable service model from Rug-Pull with RobiniaSwap. WisteriaSwap was developed with a sustainable YieldFarm DeFi service with the majority of LP in the protocol by applying the DeFi 2.0 system.
